    <item>
      <title>合氣道進步的秘訣【第0171回】　稽古，始於「做不到」之處</title>
      <link>https://kaku-budo.github.io/blog/aikido/tips/part-0101-0200/t-0171-one-is-infinite/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 11 Jan 2026 19:29:00 +0800</pubDate>
